These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lemon, lettuce, cherry
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, fish, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, scooter, motorbike
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the goat is between the person driving the scooter and the person eating lemon##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is the owner of the fish##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | lettuce | cherry  | lemon | eggplant  |
| Pet         | rabbit    | goat  | goldfish       | fish     |
| Transport   | scooter     | bike | motorbike       | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, hiking, puzzles, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, thriller, mystery, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, skiing, rugby
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
5. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | hiking | sudoku    | collecting  | puzzles |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | adventure  | thriller   | mystery    |
| Sport         | volleyball | rugby | parkour | skiing      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving, reading, drawing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, disco, hip-hop, d&b
1. the fan of disco is between the fan of d&b and the person drinking iced-tea##2
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
6. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk         | almond-milk   | juice    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | drawing | rock-climbing | reading |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | disco        | d&b      | jazz   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, chinese, colombian, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, water-polo, weightlifting, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, airplane, quad-bike
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the quad-bike and the indonesian##2
3. the colombian is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the colombian is on the right of the american##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian        | chinese   | american | colombian |
| Sport         | weightlifting | soccer | water-polo    | sailing |
| Transport     | airplane       | roller     | quad-bike       | bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, water, coffee, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, collecting, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, snowboarding, volleyball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##2
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite      | water       | coffee   |
| Hobby      | cooking   | video-games  | dancing | collecting     |
| Sport      | snowboarding     | sailing | volleyball        | weightlifting |

