.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, lemon, cabbage, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, cooking, dancing, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, badminton, baseball, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's sport is baseball##2
6. the person eating lemon is between the person eating pumpkin and the person eating cabbage##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cabbage | lemon  | pumpkin | cauliflower      |
| Hobby   | dancing  | traveling  | magic-tricks | cooking |
| Sport   | weightlifting | golf | badminton | baseball     |

