.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, kiwi, peas, spinach
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, action, crime, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, snowboarding, rowing, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching action movies##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
6. the person eating kiwi is between the person watching action movies and the person watching crime movies##2
7. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | peas  | kiwi    | spinach | zucchini  |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | romance       | action        | fantasy    |
| Sport         | snowboarding | climbing | sailing  | rowing |

