.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, puzzles, skydiving
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, superhero, romance, adventure
4 different pets are kept: snake, frog, bird, chinchilla
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | hiking | puzzles | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | adventure | superhero   | romance         |
| Pet           | snake | bird  | frog   | chinchilla      |

