.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, broccoli, onion, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, singing, gardening, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, trance, folk, gospel
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person eating raspberry##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person eating broccoli##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the fan of folk and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | papaya  | raspberry    | onion | broccoli       |
| Hobby         | dancing | singing | cooking  | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | gospel      | trance  | indie     |

