1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
3. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating peas and the person who's hobby is camping##2
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
7. the person watching satire movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person watching epic movies is the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
