.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, artichoke, cucumber, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, sudoku, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, hedgehog, ferret
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is the person eating artichoke##1
3. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the owner of the cat and the person eating cherry##2
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | cherry  | cucumber | grapefruit | artichoke     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku   | filmmaking  | writing    |
| Pet     | chinchilla        | ferret       | cat      | hedgehog |

