The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, fishing
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, hamster, horse
1. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | water     | milk | coffee       |
| Hobby      | reading  | fishing | cooking  | magic-tricks |
| Pet        | horse  | ferret      | hamster        | fish      |

