4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
