The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, animation, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, subway, quad-bike
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person driving the subway is the engineer##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fisherman##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person watching animation movies and the engineer##2
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the helicopter is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | freelancer | analyst | engineer    | fisherman   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation      | documentary   | musical | comedy |
| Transport     | boat     | helicopter       | subway        | quad-bike    |

