.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, techno, reggae, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, russian, egyptian, brazilian
1. the fan of house is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the russian##2
3. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of techno##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the fan of reggae and the brazilian##2
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the polish is between the egyptian and the fan of folk##2
7. the fan of house is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | tea   | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | house  | techno    | reggae   | folk     |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | egyptian | polish | russian   |

