.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, water
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, watermelon, cranberry, apricot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, handball, skiing, sailing
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cranberry is between the person drinking water and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
7. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola    | hot-chocolate | water           | milk |
| Food       | pumpkin | cranberry    | watermelon          | apricot   |
| Sport      | skiing  | handball   | sailing | surfing  |

