.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, juice, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, adventure, zombie, martial-arts
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, pony, dog
1. the person watching zombie movies is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the owner of the dog is between the person drinking coffee and the owner of the rabbit##2
7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | juice | lemonade | coffee     | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | martial-arts        | zombie  | adventure  |
| Pet           | rabbit      | dog         | turtle | pony |

