The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, water-polo, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, snowmobile, boat
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the architect##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the lawyer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the engineer##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person driving the boat is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the snowmobile##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | lawyer        | engineer  | architect | nurse   |
| Sport       | handball | lacrosse | water-polo    | sailing |
| Transport   | airplane        | snowmobile     | boat       | tram      |

