.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, grapes, peach, mango
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, mouse, fish
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, tram, car, quad-bike
1. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is the owner of the fish##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the person eating mango and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | mango | grapes | radish | peach |
| Pet         | turtle       | rabbit     | mouse   | fish   |
| Transport   | subway | tram | car | quad-bike |

 